comments.content: Authentic is similar to A&S Snapper Script...
Hmm, A&S Snapper Script is close, but the edges come out really jagged :/

May be [Ragged Brag](http://web.archive.org/web/20150416011448/http:/www.letterheadfonts.com/fonts/raggedbrad.php) for the script and [Futura](http://web.archive.org/web/20150416011448/http:/www.myfonts.com/search/futura) squooshed for "MEXICAN FOOD #1".
